Based on Chat server for Node.js (Copyright (c)2011-2012 Rooftop Solutions, thanks to Boy Baukema )
===================================================================================================

Requirements: nodejs
Uses: google.maps api

Note
====
Added code from the WherAmI sample from google.
Work in progress !!

Objective
=========
Allow users of mobile devices to chat when they are close to each other


Instructions
============

1. cd server
2. node ChatServer.js
3. Open http://loclahost:1337/client/index.html in a browser
4. allow the browser to access the phone gps
5. login and wait
6. chat


